---

# Agent Rules

- All agents inherit from `BaseAgent` in `agents/base.py`
- Every agent must have `name` (str) and `description` (str) class attributes
- Implement `async def handle(self, message: Message) -> None`
- After implementation, register in `agents/registry.py`
- Use `self._bus` for inter-agent messaging, `self._fleet` for LLM, `self._memory` for memory
- Log significant events with `self._log`
- Never do blocking I/O — all methods are async
